[171.642112, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[36B\u001b[38;2;177;185;249m/review-fix-ship                                            (total-recall) Use when asked to \"review and improve\", \"review ; fix ; commit\", \"harden and ship\", or any iterative\r\u001b[62C\u001b[1Breview-fix-ship loop on a git repository. Drives a closed loop until git status is clean вҖ” read the code, propose fixes with вҖҰ\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m/code-review                                                Review the current diff for correctness bugs and reuse/simplification/efficiency cleanups at the given effort level\r\u001b[62C\u001b[1B(low/medium: fewer, high-confidence findings; highвҶ’max: broader coverage, may include uncertain findings; ultra: deep multi-aвҖҰ\u001b[39m\u001b[45;1H\u001b[42;4H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[171.693385, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[3C\u001b[5B\u001b[38;2;255;193;7m11 setup i\u001b[15Gsues: MCP\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m В· /doctor\u001b[39m\u001b[45;1H\u001b[42;4H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
